com.interpss.opf

Interface BaseOpfBranch

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfBranch, Branch, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBranch, IAclfBranchAdaptation, IAclfBranchAdjustment, IAclfBranchFunc, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DclfOpfBranch, OpfBranch
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseOpfBranchImpl, DclfOpfBranchImpl, OpfBranchImpl

    public interface BaseOpfBranch
extends AclfBranch
    A representation of the model object 'Base Opf Branch'. OPF base branch class for OPF analysis.

    The following features are supported:

    • Rating Mw1
    • Rating Mw2
    • Rating Mw3
    See Also:
    OpfPackage.getBaseOpfBranch()
